CONCEALED CARRY chased between into the first turn, had a perfect set up watching the top two engage down the backstretch, angled four wide to look the main threat but could not find more to gain on the winner to the finish line. KEEP GRINDING broke sharp to have a short lead in the beginning, contested up front on the rail down the back straight, hounded the winner inside on the far turn, was in with a chance on the fence turning for home but was outfinished in the final furlong. ENCHANT ME travelled near the rear three wide in the early going, stalked on the rail at the half, was roused making little impact on the far turn, angled out five wide for the drive but could not get involved. TRINITY PARK trailed four deep in the first turn, continued to see the field inside down the back straight, put in a mild advance three eighths from home but could not reach contention running to the wire. THREE SONNY SIDEUP had an awkward start hopping at the break, tracked four wide outside into the first turn, rated outside near the rear down the backside, was ridden to go on three furlongs from the wire, could not offer a response and was not a factor through the stretch.

BODACIOUS MISS was on hold sitting on the rail behind the contesting top two at the half, lost some momentum inside with three furlongs to run and could not find another gear to be a serious threat on the fence down the stretch. NO WHAMMIE set the fractions having a narrow lead on the rail down the backside, was collared outside by runners midway on the turn, battled until mid stretch inside and backed away in the final furlong.
